verbose_text: The detected high favorable values of TDeltaS ++ (> 40 kJ/mol) indicated that binding of NIH45-46 and VRC01 to ZM-96 Env protein was accompanied by an increase in the disorder of the system, most probably mediated by a disruption of ordered solvent shells surrounding interacting proteins.
evidence: binding of NIH45-46 and VRC01 to ZM-96 Env protein
